name: Viking Life
description: You are an ordinary Viking. Your task is to gather a squad and attack other settlements, after each victory you will have a choice of 4 abilities, each with a unique pumping or talent. After death, you lose all skills and troops.

name: Fruit Girl Kiss
description: A beautiful girl with a bunch of fruit puzzles and you who are racking your brains to solve these mysteries, what kind of sparks will you create? Please wait and see!

name: Project Three
description: Project Three is a fan-made sequel to Half-Life 2: Episode Two, inspired by Mark Laidlaw's Epistle 3 script, which was adjusted and refined by fans to fit the cooperative story campaign.

name: Blitz GT
description: Blitz GT is a vehicular battle game. Battle 4v4 with unique characters and abilities to score points, take down opponents and secure the win.

name: Resident Evil 2
description: The GameBoy Advance version of Resident Evil 2 was a tech demo created in 2003 by Raylight Studios, an Italian company to pitch their Blue Roses engine. By this point in time Capcom had lost interest in the viability of GameBoy ports, and the pitch was rejected.

name: Deadrop
description: Deadrop is a vertical extraction shooter (VES). With a focus on Arena style combat, battle royale sized lobbies and vertical extraction. A unique first person shooter where one must climb to the tippy top if they want to be the best and find the best loot. Shooting other players and other ai at the same time.

name: Duck Adventure
description: A game released for the Mega Duck/Cougar Boy in 1993.

name: Bounty Star
description: Bounty Star is an over-the-shoulder 3D action game that marries mech combat and customization with farming and base building. The player takes on the role of a broken but powerful ex-soldier named Clem, a war veteran, talented fighter and expert mech pilot.

name: Outlaw Racing
description: Outlaw Racing is an unreleased racing game for the Sega VR headset.

name: Iron Hammer
description: Iron Hammer is an unreleased tank combat game for the Sega VR headset.

name: Bulls and Cows
description:
Bulls and cows is an ancient puzzle game of password cracking.
Take advantage of limited opportunities to guess a random four digit number. Every time you guess, you can get a prompt about whether the number and position are correct, until you guess the correct answer (victory), or use up all opportunities (failure). According to different difficulty and guess times, corresponding points will be obtained.

name: Sauna 2000
description: Story driven comedic Sauna Simulator / Mystery Horror Game. Heat a Finnish sauna without actually going to Finland.

name: Equestrian the Game
description: Equestrian the game is a horse riding, management, and breeding game. Ride, compete, and breed horses of different breeds and personalities!

name: The Idle Undead
description:
The Idle Undead is an Idle Clicker game set in a Zombie Apocalypse!
Click to defeat enemies, get loot and cash and spend it to upgrade your base and recruit survivors to help you in your survival.
Gameplay
The Idle Undead is a clicker game where you recruit survivors and purchase various upgrades to progress, You start by clicking on the screen to earn points, that you spend to recruit fellow survivors to defeat the enemies around you!
Enemies drop various rewards, such as XP and Cash you put towards levelling up to unlock new areas and upgrades, with more advanced features unlocking the further you progress.

Boosts - These are unlocked at Level 10, and provide you with the ability to get temporary boosts that boost your production for a limited time!

Base Upgrades - You can level up your base with various upgrades to help you in-game!

Cards - Open crates dropped after bosses to earn cards, These cards provide an effect when used and are then destroyed, You can strategize when to use these to help you in difficult situations

Enemy Attacks - Enemies can fight back and can attack the player when spawned by putting various effects on the player that make your gameplay more difficult!
Story
The game is set several years after the outbreak of a virus that transforms the population into mutated zombie-like creatures, Originating amongst the wealthy who spread the virus slowly down to the common population, it's true origin is unknown, but the mutated creatures show plant like roots within them.
Find newspapers and additional lore as you progress in game to get the full story!

Find tapes throughout your playthrough to play visual-novel like sequences that let you experience the outbreak in various ways through the eyes of different people

name: Cyber Lancer
description:
Pilot the Hyper-Advanced, mechanized assault suit: Cyber Lancer.

Purchase and upgrade weapons to take down waves upon waves of enemies!

Feast your eyes on Mind-Melting Sega Saturn inspired graphics!

name: My name is Uter
description: Are you want to play with a toy? Oh, sorry... I mean Do you want to play as a toy? Well, then this game is made for you. The great adventure is waiting for you.

name: SolChicks
description:
SolChicks Saga is a play-to-earn ("P2E") multiplayer role-playing game where the players' unique SolChicks NFTs are used as their game characters.

Players can participate in SolChicks Saga in multiple ways, be it leveling their characters through participating in PvE or PvP challenges, farming the rarest items and seeking hidden treasures, or even just treating your SolChicks as virtual pets to pass time. Amongst the key differentiating factors is that SolChicks Saga is NFT driven where the SolChick NFT will act as the player's in-game avatar.

name: Village of Origins
description: RPG storytelling and hack-and-slash action, are joined with a retro point and click play style. Command a diverse array of hosts, and engage in fast-paced combat that rewards skill and strategy instead of grinding.

name: Bake it Till' You Make it!
description: Bake it Till' You Make it is a cooking/sandbox game. You can bake treats, decorate cakes, and basically do whatever you want. Your kitchen has a wide variety of tools and ingredients from sprinkles, piping bags, and flamethrowers. The room also includes a large selection of multiple sprinkle colors and many ovens. You can grab one of the four cake types: loaves, bundts, cupcakes, and regular cakes and cook them inside of the oven. The cakes all have different cooking temperatures and times. Cook with caution as cooking cakes for extended periods of time could cause them to burn. You can also use the piping bag and color pipettes to apply frosting onto four different kinds of cakes. The frosting will then stick on the cake and allow for the cake to be transported. Sprinkles can then be shaken over the cake to add more decoration to the cake. The game is currently in early access and more tools and ingredients are planned and will be added in the future.

name: Shadow of Witch Marionette
description: Shadow of Witch Marionette is a direct sequel to 2019's WitchSpring4 following Eirudy the Marionette Witch inside the Shadow World.

name: My Universe: Pet Clinic - Cats & Dogs: Panda Edition
FNaC Fur
description: This is the game. put down your silly horror games and join Candy and his twin sister Cindy on this brand new adventure - a spiritual successor to "Candy's Adventure", a popular minigame from the hit horror experience "Five Nights at Candy's 3"!

name: Birds of Paradise
description:
Fresh out of college, Robin thinks she’s hit the jackpot after landing a position as assistant manager to the Birds of Paradise; an upcoming boy band with dreams of making it big. Robin is thrilled to be working with such high-profile clients… though not everything is as glamorous as it first seems.

Not only must Robin navigate her relationships with the Birds of Paradise and the Birds of Prey, but she must ensure both she and the band succeed... in life, love, and in the limelight!

name: Ben 10: Alien Force Game Creator
description: Create 2D stages with enemies, objects, and playable characters from Cartoon Network's TV show, "Ben 10: Alien Force"

name: Cartoon Network Universe: Project Exonaut
description: Was a multiplayer online PVP online shooter featuring 48 suits split into the Atlas Brigade and Banzai Squadron, 6 original and 42 based on characters across the Cartoon Network lineup.

name: Teen Titans: Calling All Titans
description: Top-down adventure game where minigames determine the outcome of battles against enemies.

name: The Fairly OddParents: Battle of the Futurebots
description: In the future robots will replace humans in daily routine things and Timmy wants to get rid of boring chore as soon as possible. Well, dream often come true, but future he wanted to have doesn't match with reality. His friends are now the slaves of the big brain and he has to release them using a robot. Build your own robot and the junk and install the parts you feel will be better for your playing style!

name: Error Found
description: ERROR FOUND is a genre-redefining psychological horror game that takes place in a seemingly normal clicker game. When a previously normal game gets hijacked by a character, players are forced to find the truth within the game and make decisions that will forever impact their gameplay.

name: Inn Keeper
description: Embody, in a unique first-person management game experience, an innkeeper in a rich medieval-fantasy world. Manage your establishment based on your own rules and choose which path you want to follow. Adapt to your customers and achieve a thriving economy. Build your own inn down to the last detail and spread your influence across the world.

name: Dancing Onigiri
description: Dancing☆Onigiri is an open-source Japanese web browser rhythm game that is currently written with Javascript, HTML and CSS, and was formerly made using Flash. This game contains charts of various keymodes such as 5key, 7key, 11key, etc. that are either played static or dynamic, all community made! You can even create your own charts and even keymodes, provided that you know how!

name: Gadkiy Ya 2
description: Despicable Me 2 is a bootleg video game for the Sega Mega Drive based on the movie of the same name.

name: Darkwing Duck
description: Darkwing Duck is a bootleg port of the NES version of Darkwing Duck for Sega Genesis.

name: Sonic R/Sonic 3D
description: Sonic R/Sonic 3D is a bundle consisting of Sonic R and Sonic 3D: Flickies' Island for Windows PCs, released in the UK under the Xplosiv brand.

name: Sonic Saturn
description: Alongside the production of Sonic X-treme, STI was working on another game only known as "Sonic Saturn". Rather than use sprites for sonic, though, it was going to use a 3D model for Sonic. This game was meant to have a more realistic rendition of Sonic's world than X-treme. It was never actually announced publicly that it was in production, but didn't get very far before being canceled.

name: Sonic Riders
description:
Sonic Riders was a port of Sonic Riders to the Game Boy Advance. It was in development at the same time as the other Sonic Riders ports. The game used a Out-Run style game engine. When Sega of Japan insisted on adding more 3D to the game it was cancelled by Sega of USA as it could not be completed within the tight production schedule.

Info on the game was discovered on Keith Erickson’s portfolio and Arvin Bautista’s resume.

name: Ben 10: Galactic Racing
description: It's a galactic race to the finish as Ben, Kevin and twelve of Ben's alien heroes join an interplanetary Galactic Grand Prix in Ben 10 Galactic Racing, an action-packed game now available on all platforms. This is the first Ben 10 game to be a racing game.

name: Kitty's Catch
description: Kitty's Catch is a cancelled NES game created by GameTek employee David Wiebenson in his spare time. Wiebenson pitched Kitty's Catch to several publishers, all of which refused to publish the game. Eventually, several prototypes were discovered and purchased in a lot by the Nolan brothers, who released the most complete ROM to the public. Kitty's Catch is a two-player game where players control cats named Pitter and Patter, and have to catch fish with their tails. The first player to fill their bucket with fish gets a shell, and the player with the most shells at the end of the time limit wins. There are also several power-ups obtained by collecting tin cans, such as larger hooks.

name: Jodie Drake
description: Jodie travels the world taking pictures of treasures and artifacts for a prestigious travel magazine. Help her explore 64 exotic locations and find hundreds of hidden artifacts.

name: Lara's Mysterious Restorations
description: Lana Vassari restores well known paintings by finding and revealing mysterious objects hidden within layers of paint. Help her earn money to decorate her apartment.

name: The Broken Clues 2
description: Work with a seasoned investigator to search for hidden the richest man in town.

name: Dominic Cranes's Dreamscape Mystery
description: Travel through eerie worlds and navigate through a maze of puzzles to uncover the meaning behind Dominic Crane's mysterious dreams in this hidden object puzzle!

name: Treasure Island: The Gold Bag
description: The year is 1827 when William Legrand, the son of a wealthy family from New Orleans, lost everything. Ashamed, he leaves and creates a home on Sullivan's Island near Charleston, South Carolina. Here he lives simply and peacefully, until one day when he discovers a golden beetle on the beach which will set him on a journey in search of Captain Kidd's hidden treasure! Guide William on the adventure of a lifetime in Treasure Island: The Golden Bug!

name: The Hidden Prophecies of Nostradamus
description: A curse based on Nostradamus' quatrains predicts the deaths of 12 members of the Royal family. Ancient tarot cards lead you to the missing fragments of his crystal ball.

name: Stranded in the Amazon
description: With the help of a ghost, search a derelict ship stranded inthe jungle to uncover an astonishing mystery.

name: Lord of Nightmares
description: Angela Young loses her cat Felix in a dream world where the Lord of Nightmares rules. With the help of a mysterious wizard she sets out to find Felix and stop the evil Lord. Help Angela navigate her own dreamscapes in this fantastical Hidden Object adventure.

name: Macabre Mysteries: Curse of the Nightingale
Madeline and the Magnificent Puppet Show: A Learning Journey
Legends 2: Hidden Relics
description:
Mystery, intrigue and adventure! These three hidden object adventures will take you to exotic spots around the world where you'll solve challenging mysteries. The bundle includes;
- The Broken Clues 2
- Lara's Mysterious Restorations
- Jodie Drake

name: Legends in Time
description:
Legends In Time features three hidden object games:
- Dominic Cranes's Dreamscape Mystery
- Memorabilia
- Yard Sale Junkie.
These three new hidden object adventures will take you to exotic spots around the world where you'll search for 1000's of hidden objects, solve challenging puzzles and uncover intriguing mysteries.

name: Legends of Terror Collection
description: Experience a wide variety of horror stories in this collection of 20 complete mysteries

name: JumpStart Pet Party
description: A cancelled JumpStart title for the Nintendo DS.

name: Kids Learn and Play: Pets and Vets Bundle
Jericho Mirage
description: Puzzle game developed for the EA Pogo free-to-play casual game service.

name: John Deere American Farmer: Deluxe Edition
John Deere: Busy Days in Deerfield Valley
John Deere: North American Farmer
description:
John Deere: North American Farmer is the sequel to the farming simulation, John Deere: American Farmer. Like most sequels, there is much of the same content from the original game with the addition of updates and new features.

There is new John Deere equipment, enhanced weather effects, new structures and additional farm animals. There are 10 new scenarios that add to the challenge of planning, building and managing a successful farm.

name: Jack's House
description: It's a world of wonder and imagination, designed especially for children ages 2-8. From the moment your kids come over to play, they will be filled with delight. First they will meet Jack and truly lovable character who's hapy to show them aroiund. Jack's House uses a point and click format which teached hand-eye coordination. and each click revals a delightful surprise. They will learn the alphabet, color dinosaurs, sing a song, read a bonus storybook and learn about the Solar System, the change of seasons and more!! It is a game filled with joy and wonder for kids and the entire family.

name: Mon Coach Personnel: J'ameliore Mon Anglais
Rock Hoppers
description: A light-hearted but deep first person exploration and survival, base builder game for you and your friends set in a procedurally-generated asteroid belt on the edge of known space. Explore the world, learn new skills, build and defend your base, and conquer the belt's unique threats.

name: Nara: Facing Fire
description: In a world where a mysterious energy known as Va flows through and connects all living beings, a child with the power to command this energy was born. As the last of her kind, young Nara must unravel the dark secrets of her power and face the flames and shadows that took someone special from her.

name: Isla Dorada: Episode 1 - The Sands of Ephranis
Margrave Manor 3: The Curse of the Blacksmith's Heart
Neverwinter Nights: Gold Edition
description:
This Edition contains the original award winning Neverwinter Nights, with the latest updates and patches, as well as the first expansion pack, Neverwinter Nights: Shadows of Undrentide.
The package also contains a couple of "mini-adventures", created by Bioware's employees. "The Winds of Eremor" and "The Dark Ranger's Treasure" are mods by Rob Bartel, and "The Heir is Human" was created by Dan Whiteside.

name: NHRA Drag Racing: Pro Stock Cars & Trucks
NHRA Drag Racing: Quarter Mile Showdown
Nickelodeon Nick O Matic Design Factory
Final Fantasy: Blackmoon Prophecy II
description: One hundred years after the events of Blackmoon Prophecy, the world of Gaia has recovered from the conflict with Emperor Belmont, Malacore, and Zeul which saw a group of adventurers, today known as the Light Warriors, save the world from certain doom.

name: Final Fantasy: Blackmoon Prophecy
description: This is a Final Fantasy fangame that is meant to emulate the first six entries of the series. Aside from just being a fangame, Blackmoon Prophecy is also a tribute to Final Fantasy in the sense that the developer tried to put together many of the things he loved about playing RPGs growing up into this game. It's a love letter to retro gaming and our childhoods.

name: Ni-Hao Kai-Lan: Kai-Lan's Great trip to China!
Iron John Hawk: The Shards Of Power
Payne Stewart Golf
description:
Payne Stewart Pro Golf is an unreleased golf game for the Sega Mega Drive set to be published by Time Warner Interactive.
The game demoed at Winter CES 1995 with a tenative Spring 1995 release date. The project was cancelled for unknown reasons.
Two prototypes were released by Hidden Palace on January 1, 2022.

name: The Journeyman Project: Pegasus Prime
description: Originally announced as a "Director's Cut", It was released solely for the Power Macintosh by Bandai Digital Entertainment in North America. It contained a 4 disk set which required disk swapping during gameplay. There were plans to port the game to the PlayStation (with publisher Acclaim Entertainment) and Sega Saturn in the U.S., but these versions were never released. As a result, original disks of the Mac-only game have been very rare to find.

name: Jumanji: A Jungle Adventure Game Pack
Jewel Craft
description: Swap beautiful jewels and break them for new jewels! This match-3 game is ready to give you tremendous experience of speed and tension. Take this spacecraft and challenge the highest score ever!

name: PGA Tour Pro: Classic Courses Volume 1
Weaver
description: A daily word game, based on Lewis Carroll's word ladder. Players must change one word into another valid word, one letter at a time, until they have made the target word.

name: Picture Puzzle Collection: The Dutch Masters
Quadrobat
description: Quadrobat is a precision platformer with unique movement. Using a grapple you can swing through the world with speed and momentum.

name: TinyArmored
description: Progress through various land and defeat all enemies that are in your way. Collect resource, upgrade and customize your vehicle like you want.

name: Prank'd: Prank Your Way Around the World
The Lord of the Rings: Heroes of Middle Earth
description:
A new adventure is brewing in The Lord of the Rings: Heroes of Middle-earth!

Soon you will be able to seize the power of the New Ring and rewrite history. Good or evil - the choice will be yours…

name: The Football T
description: Dribble the ball to become the best football player in the world.

name: Kloa: Child of the Forest
description: Consumed by a mysterious curse, restore a once lush forest and its inhabitants to their natural state in this action adventure tale. Experience fast-paced combat, puzzles, and the beauty of nature captured in handcrafted pixel art.

name: Professor Iris' Fun Field Trip: Animal Safari
Prince of Persia Collection: Limited Edition
description:
This collection includes:
- Prince of Persia
- Prince of Persia 2: The Shadow & The Flame
- A video about the making of Prince of Persia 3D

name: Pro Bass Fishing
description: Its a game about fishing published by the makers of D!Zone, Perdition's Gate, Duke It Out In D.C, and many more well remembered video games.

name: Professor Iris' Fun Field Trip: Seaside Adventure
Pufu's Spiral: Adventures Around the World
Fell Seal: Arbiter's Mark - Deluxe Edition
description: Fell Seal: Arbiter’s Markis is set in the fantastical world of Teora, which was torn asunder centuries ago. The world has mostly recovered under the guidance of the ruling Immortal Council, yet it is still fraught with danger. As Kyrie, an Arbiter serving the Council, you’ll be tasked with protecting the land’s people from these dangers. However, a darker current runs beneath the surface — Kyrie discovers the corruption festering within her own order and comes to question the motives of Teora’s would-be protectors.

name: Kohan: Immortal Sovereigns Special Awards Edition
description:
The first game in the Kohan series packaged in a new Game of the Year edition. The GOTY edition comes with 12 new maps, 13 brand new heroes, 16 new computer strategies, and an improved computer A.I.

The game is set in a fantasy world where you take on the role of an immortal known as the Kohan. Your race once ruled the world, but was devastated in a series of cataclysms. As an immortal you have reawakened to a new world, unlike the one you once knew. If you are to return your race to their rightful glory you must solve the mystery of their destruction.

name: 2 Game Pack I Hallowed Legends: Samhain & Hallowed Legends: Templar
Bolt Bot Screwy Viruses
description: Take control of a robot named Bolt in over 50 levels of 3D platforming fun inspired by 90's and early 2000's classic platform games. It is a collect-a-thon at heart and rewards the player constantly in an evolving hub world!

name: Great Battles of the American Civil War
MeetLight and the Secrets of the Universe
description: MeetLight is an indie RPG, with crafting, farming, building, and a unique spiritual story. Run your forge by day, take care of your farm and trade with the villagers then explore the energetical worlds and meet their inhabitants at night!

name: Furius Legacy
description: Furius Legacy is an MMORPG based on blockchain. An entire metaverse with plenty of magic creatures. You can earn and sell your gold ($FLG). It is a world where you can gather friends, create guilds, raise your character and fight in pvp and ESports Battle.

name: Go Fish! The Pop n' Drop Game
Reading Recipes: Grandma Ollie's Morphabet Soup
The Nova Era
description:
"The Nova Era" is a survival construction game with the theme of alien exploration.
The story takes place in the future, the earth's resources will be exhausted, and human beings have to find a new home. After long-term research by scientists, they finally found a planet suitable for human survival. This planet is Proxima b.
The radiation on Proxima b will have a bad effect on the human body, adults cannot survive under the radiation of Proxima b. However, scientists have found that children are not affected by the radiation. Players will play as a child who goes to explore Proxima b, and need to build fortifications and use powerful weapons to resist the attack of bugs and complete difficult tasks.

name: Cataline
description: Blast your way through the embroidered world of Cataline!

name: Haru Ichiban
description:
Haru Ichiban, in Japanese, means « The wind of Spring ».
In the Emperor’s gardens, spring slowly awakens nature. The carps, frogs and dragonflies warm up under the first rays of the sun.
Two apprentice gardeners are competing to see which one will earn the enviable duty of Imperial Gardener. They will show their skills and try to profit from this first wind of Spring to have the water lilies blossom in their color while making the most harmonious combinations !
The goal of the game is to make the water lilies blossom and move them using the breeze of the first wind of Spring, in order to form harmonious geometric figures (alignments or groupings of flowers of your color) worthing victory points.
Haru Ichiban has been designed by Bruno Cathala, a well-known french boardgame designer, who has still published more than 40 games.

name: Mini Leap
description:
Mini is lost and all alone in the big city. Help Mini get home by collecting enough coins and dodging obstacles through various stages. Play in Challenge Mode or Endless Mode.
Hang tight, more fun stages are coming soon!

name: Angry Bulls
description: Angry Bulls is a racing & action game that it is easy to control has thrill sense and has been getting hi-ranking and craze in players all over the world.The fun and anger effects added in the game play where Bull is Angry and out of control with having full of anger, avoid the obstacles such as horrible small fence and hell rings and to get gold and item by controlling rapidly the hi-speedy running was crazy to low down his anger by hitting animals come in his way, makes users have a good fun.

name: Coastline
description: Coastline is a fast paced first person parkour game. With a heavy emphasis on platforming and a bit of soft core combat mixed in, Coastline is extremely engaging and rewards the best players who understand the depth of the abilities, combat encounters, and more!

name: Death Slave
description: Death Slave is a 2D puzzle-platformer where the player must intelligently kill their character in different ways to gain new powers to solve platforming challenges.

name: Faith & Shield: Tower Defense - Space Wars Game 2022
description: The remaining survivors realized that if they will continue like this, there would be no more of them as a species, so they decided to give all their efforts and create the last bastion of faith. Everything is not lost yet, but something unexpected comes…

name: Mini Subway: Logic on the Metro Line
description: Remember that the growth of the city is random, so each game will be unique! Mini Subway: Logic on the Metro Line is a game in which you will design the subway station network of a city. Trace different lines between stations and put all your trains i…

name: Driving Quest
description: In Driving Quest you will rediscover the joy of driving! Explore a breathtaking environment and accomplish a variety of challenging & exciting missions!

name: Japanese Escape Games: The Hotel of Tricks
Super Kenney
description: A relaxed and enjoyable platform jumping puzzle adventure game, come and complete the adventure with Kenney! ! !

name: Noodle Party
description: A trivia party game with a high range of questions and multiple minigames along the way. Compete against friends or family, with up to 4 players locally! Prove you are the smartest noodle!

name: Pizza Delivery Bagel
description: Work the most insane pizza delivery job of all time, and try to make as much money as possible before you get fired!

name: DoDodge2020
description: a simple bullet dodge game with customizable content.

name: Tiki Tiki Hop
description: "TikiTikiHop" is a cartoon style casual game. The game is easy to operate and suitable for playing for a while in your spare time.

name: Box Runner!
description: "Box Runner! " is a 2D platform jumping game, the game is simple to operate, the atmosphere is relaxed, and the cartoon picture is suitable for casual play for a while.

name: Faustian Bargain
description: Faustian Bargain, first-person horror game that brings a new and different twist to the thriller and survival-horror genres. After the Ouija sessions, immerse yourself in the tragedies of the victims and a story between reality and the supernatural. Play a hero whose life is between dark and light.

name: Earth's Center of Gravity
description: Earth's Center of Gravity is a mystic horror visual novel with multiple endings. The story revolves around Tower Antiques. "No one remembers how long Tower Antiques was there. But it remembers everyone. Even the ones who did not visit it yet." Tower Antiques is waiting for you to write your story.

name: Animal Shelter Simulator: Puppies & Kittens
description: This time our pupils in the shelter will be small dogs and kittens. In this unique DLC, you'll be able to look after kittens and puppies from an early age. There will also be tons of other great features in the DLC, check it out for yourself!

name: Acassia
description: Tank, action and shooting game, where does it start your new adventure in a world of science fiction and interplanetary wars...

name: Jumping!
description: Jumping！ is a side-scrolling pixel-jumping game that allows you to experience how to avoid falling platforms by jumping on your PC.

name: Tropi
description: Tropi is a horizontally-scrolling shoot 'em up set in the Caribbean Sea. You play as the titular Tropi. With the help of his friend and caretaker, Carmen, the two must go out and fight against aliens who have from sprung from the Bermuda Triangle and are terrorizing the surrounding area.

name: Hiddenverse: The Iron Tower
description: Help Sarah sneak into the Iron Tower and sabotage the evil lord's dark devices.

name: Nom Nom Nom
description: A delicious arcade game of eating and drinking.

name: Soulframe
description:
This free-to-play open world adventure heavily influenced by themes of nature, restoration, and exploration.

Soulframe will deliver its own independent and uniquely immersive experience led by the creative and imaginative minds behind Warframe.

name: Diamond Skee-Ball
description: Diamond Skee-Ball is a Twitch chat game for all streamer to play from the comfort of your home.

name: Front Page Sports: Golf - Black Diamond Ranch
The Evidence
description: In The Evidence you'll take over the role of a detective who has to search for evidence at crime scenes and identify the possible murderer. Use your sharp mind and find the connections to solve the case!

name: Mary Kate and Ashley's Dance Party of the Century
Math-A-Thon 2: The Mystery of the Missing Laboratory
Math Missions: The Amazing Arcade Adventure Grades 3-5
Math Missions: The Race to Spectacle City Arcade K-2
Knights of Decayden
description:
Knights of Decayden is a rediscovered (July 2022) title, a long-lost exclusive release for the original Xbox. It was developed by the team behind a series of acclaimed Star Wars games and quietly canceled by Microsoft two decades ago.

Knights of Decayden (sometimes spelled as Decadyn) has been largely unknown to the public until now and helps highlight a hidden part of early Xbox history.

The game went by many names, including Knights of Utu, when it was pitched in 2000 to Sony as a PlayStation 2 game. Ultimately it became an Xbox exclusive until it's cancellation.

name: Millionaire Manor, Robin's Quest, Escape the Lost Kingdom and the Hidden Object Show 2
Mind Medley
description: Mind Medley is a collection of casual mini-games for the PC designed to challenge memory and attentiveness.

name: Bob: A thousand lives
description: Discover Bob's variable and unique world, get to know his story and support him to reach his goal which is non other than finding his ultimate peace. Be a part of the cycle in which death and reborning are present countless times almost at the same time.

name: Invadead
description: shoot at hordes of zombies using diffrent guns and grenades, epicly decimating them by your pure handsomeness.

name: Battle Part
description: 3D Vehicles Shooter focused on boss battles.

name: Neko Cosmo Police
description: This twin stick shooter is about Neko fighting with their all cost. In 2565 UC. the Cosmos has been altered by MadBotz gang. The last hope is rely on the Neko Cosmo Police team, "Kuro" and "Shiro"

name: Metapilot
description: Designed with top experts from Boeing, the UK Government and several EVTOL companies, Metapilot gives you the real EVTOL flight experience! Fly your aircraft around the city, pick up guests from skyscrapers on time and don't run out of fuel! Bring the future one step closer by playing Metapilot now.

name: The Tsar's Secret
description: An indie stealth game about outsmarting your enemies by altering the senses. Would you rather blind or deafen your enemies?

name: Gunstars
description:
A multiplayer Battle Royale made for mobile!

Gunstars is a fast-paced third-person shooter battle royale, where the player’s main objective is to explore the combat arenas to collect supplies and weapons to fight and be the last one standing.

Fight, explore and create the best strategy to survive epic battles with up to 36 players. Play solo or invite friends and live epic experiences within the battle arenas of the Gunstars universe.

Join competitive teams for exclusive rewards, and collect or trade NFTs with the community, all close to your favorite creators and brands.

With thirty characters to choose from, one hundred and sixty trivia questions to answer and three hundred and sixty cards to collect you'll have countless hours of card gaming action!

description: Poker Pop is a tile matching puzzle game with elements of Mahjong, Solitaire and Poker. 50 levels are included, each level is a city. By getting special combinations like full house or straight flush, you get power ups to discover the city, together with facts and trivia.

name: Poker Superstars III: Gold Chip Challenge
Isles
description: Isles is a 3D pixel world building simulation game: place tiles, manage resources and elect the leader regularly to thrive the island and build an army to fight against the invading troops. Also, many unknown islands are waited for your landing. Come and be the lord of the ISLES.

name: Hidden Shapes Animals: VR
description: Tired after a hard day at work? Now, with the help of VR, you will delve deep into an environment exclusively prepared for you to have fun and rescue your tranquility, surprising yourself with each solved puzzle!

name: Random House Puzzles & Games: Crosswords & Crostics
description: Random House Puzzles & Games: Crosswords is a compilation that consists of two separate games each containing one hundred and fifty puzzles.

name: Five Nights at Freddy's Cleaning Simulator
description: Five Nights at Freddy's Cleaning Simulator is a cancelled free-roam Five Nights at Freddy's fan-game made by Nikson for Fangames at Freddit's game jam.

name: Those Nights at Fredbear's: Reboot
description: hose Nights at Fredbear's Reboot is a discontinued official remake of the very first cancelled free-roam FNaF fan-game Nikson made. The remake features new story, new graphics, new characters etc. If you are going to use anything on this page for refrence in your fangame. Please credit the page and those who have contributed to it.

name: Hybrid Harmony
description: A romantic comedy visual novel set in a modern fantasy world filled with mythical creatures and races! Shape your story through tons of meaningful choices, text characters and unlock wallpapers using an in-depth phone system, and learn about the world and it's lore with an expansive glossary!

name: Evil Bird Simulator
description: Evil Bird Simulator is a weird pixel art game where you control an evil bird that craps on people and cars. Some of the people will try to attack you and you will go to hell if you get a game over. You will have to play your way through hell to get back to the normal game. Do you have what it takes?

name: Adventure Climb VR: Brave the Elements
description: This map pack adds five new levels to climb and explore all with varying difficulty to challenge even the most advanced climber!

name: Last Crash
description: While performing missions in a world on the verge of destruction, we try to survive by managing resources under difficult conditions with special equipment.

name: Those Nights at Rachel's 2
description:
That onslaught and terror which corrupted your very mind is only the beginning, those nightmares which tormented your brain is nothing like what we prepared.

Together we'll make your final moments something worth chanting for, something worth telling. And you- well you'll just be there to watch it all go down, sitting and staring without the ability to pick yourself up.

Tonight will be OUR night, the night in which we reign the same amount of screams and terror as we have in the past to find the one thing in which we really want

name: Unreal Shift At Freddy's
description:
Unreal Shift at Freddy's is a game inspired by the popular franchise Five Nights at Freddy's by Scott Cawthon.

It features a fully remade map from FNAF 1 in 3D and gives you the ability to free roam however you wish.

name: Those Nights at Fredbear's
description: Those Nights At Fredbear's was a free roam survival horror video game developed by Nikson. The game was cancelled, but way later on the 17th of July 2018, Nikson revealed a teaser trailer for a "Those Nights At Fredbear's" remake at the end of his anniversary Q&A video on The Joy of Creation: Story Mode.

name: Sweep Serf
description:
Sweep Serf is a 2D puzzle platformer where players must use their wit navigate through minesweeper-like obstacles and get the highest scores.

However, players have more at their disposal than just their smarts to make it through. There are lots of items to unearth and craft to solve even the toughest roadblocks - and since each run is randomly generated, you can be sure that each playthrough is a fun and unique experience!

name: Another FNaF Fangame: Open Source
description: Another FNAF Fangame: Open Source is a moddable, infinitely changeable version of FNAF 2. It can be anything you want it to be, so make it the most enjoyable horror you have ever imagined. It's a FNAF 2 with newer mechanics, new office and different settings!

name: Spellcraft
description: Spellcraft is a new type of strategy game: a Real-Time Battler where you actively command an entire team of heroes and cast spells to outplay your opponents.

name: The Real Deal: 10 Classic Card Games
Star Wars: Rebel Assault - Special Edition
Hiss
description: A twist on an old classic.

name: Red Baron Squadron
description:
Red Ace Squadron is basically a standalone add-on for Master of the Skies: The Red Ace
(or Red Ace for short). It includes the following improvements: 2 new campaigns with 14 additional missions, power-up stations to repair your plane, two new planes and multiplayer over LAN, modem and internet.

name: Mirror Chains
description: Novel match-3 gameplay + all kinds of beautiful girl characters = this game, you are welcome to challenge~

name: Versus Tactics
description: Versus Tactics is a 1v1 turn-based competitive battle game inspired by the classic Final Fantasy Tactics. Manage your levels, characters and summon to outsmart and overpower your opponents. Become the battlefield's ultimate tactician!

name: Cycle Breaker
description: Deflect bullets and take down invading robot minibosses with just your laser sword, in pursuit of the highest combo!

name: Minigolf Maniacs
description: Miniature golf is a crazy sport as it is, but Minigolf Maniacs takes the unpredictable nature of the popular pastime to new heights. There are still the standard windmill holes, castles, and the like, but the game really goes nuts by adding in touches like fire-breathing dragons, ill-willed flower patches, and dozens of hidden obstacles. Add to all of that the fact that there's a pack of mischief-making kids running around terrorizing the golfers, and you've got yourself one tense gaming experience. You choose between eight playable characters each of whom happens to be a representative of a species from the wild and make your way through 40 wacky holes. There are eight different game types to shake things up a bit, and four hidden boss characters to ensure that your game won't be easy. All of the graphics are 3D, and the game is packed with shortcuts, power-ups, and lots of other unexpected madness.

name: Missing
description:
Receive actual e-mail from virtual characters and The Phoenix himself, use these email and other evidence as clues, to put together the pieces of the puzzle.
Visit all kinds of Websites within the game to collect information and solve the case.

name: Emily Archer: The Curse of King Tut's Tomb
Reel Deal Casino: Valley of the Kings
Emo's Match Maker: The Game of Love
Return to Castle Wolfenstein: Game of the Year Edition
Tesla Legacy
description: Explore a secret facility and use the power of electricity to defeat all machines, a new VR combat experience waiting to challenge your skills.

name: A Day as a T-Rex
description:
You play as a T-Rex through a human's daily routine and in a human apartment, and you have different tasks to complete to win the game.
Examples: Making the bed, brushing teeth, showering, making breakfast, maybe T-rex is working from home and has to attend morning meetings, doing laundry, filling the dishwasher, etc. All tasks have to be solved in creative ways with minimum damage. Every task can be completed in perfection for 100%, but for example, the dishwasher, with every broken thing that is supposed to go into the washer, that percentage shrinks, and by 0%, the task fails.
The apartment is filled just as an apartment would be, and most of the stuff is intractable with physics.

The player has T-Rex limitations. Hand position will be at the player's chest and the T-Rex nose is in the way, limiting the player's view and reach. The T-rex tail can knock stuff around.
At the start of the game, the player is instructed into the proper position, and each time the player breaks position, the game pauses, or some other penalty is added.
The player wins the game by completing the whole day. The score is based on how well the player completed each task.

name: Lilly's
description:
A 2D game set in a fantasy town inspired by the 1700s France or Italy.

You play as Lilly, a young girl who is the owner of a butcher shop that sells very special types of meat. Every night Lilly goes out with the big butcher's knife to restock the shop, by murdering the citizens of the town.

Lilly has been left by herself and been through some gruesome events, she is trying to reach out to her mother. Writing letters to her, asking for help and support but also about what she is doing at night.

There are good and bad people in the town, like anywhere else. You need to keep a balance otherwise there will be consequences. You also need to be careful to not get arrested by the police, because what Lilly is doing is actually a crime.

name: Exorcist II
description: Save the world from everlasting darkness in Exorcist 2, the next terrifying chapter in the saga of Garret Ghostfighter.

name: Earth Command: The Future of Our World is in Your Hands
Ringling Bros. and Barnum & Bailey: Circus Friends - Asian Elephants
Mr. and Mrs. Potato Head Go on Vacation
Ms. Pac Person
description: Ms. Pac Person is a clone of Pac Man (or Ms. Pac Man to be more specific). Graphics aside, the game is essentially identical to the original Pac Man. Ms. MacPerson (who is controlled with the keyboard) has to make her way through a maze, collect all the pills while staying away from the four ghosts that chases her. By eating special power pill things are turned around and she can go after the ghosts who then run away. A level is completed once all pills have been collected. The player has three lives and when they are used up it's game over. Like in the arcade original there are intermissions between some of the levels.

name: Nascar Web Racing
description: Nascar Web Racing the only free NASCAR-licensed racing game on the Web. Produced by Electronic Arts online division, EA Sports Nascar Web Racing allows players to choose real NASCAR Nextel Cup Series drivers, such as Dale Earnhardt, Jr. and Jimmie Johnson; official stock cars; real NASCAR tracks (Bristol Motor Speedway, Atlanta Motor Speedway, Infineon Raceway); and real NASCAR elements, such as drafting, passing and pit stops.

name: National Geographic Lilly Wu and the Terra Cotta Mystery
Poker Pop!
description:
A new way to play solo games of poker!
Poker Pop is a domino style tile matching game where you place cards onto the board to create poker hands. Score as many points as you can before filling up the board.

name: Hell of Sins: Soul
description: Hell of Sins: Soul is a Cthulhu-style horror adventure game (AVG). The story tells that Qin Xuan, the male leading role, fell into hell after his death, and found that hell was not the legendary reincarnation place of souls, but a horrible prison with various kinds of evil ghosts--Hell of Sins.

name: First Time In Paris: Collector's Edition
description: Join amateur travel blogger Kate Robinson and her daughter Nicole as they go on their first big business trip to save a Parisian hotel!

name: Vermillion Descent
description:
After falling for what seems like forever, Dictum combat android VERSION-1.413^^10+2 finds herself in a mysterious otherworld deep below, an endless chasm devoid of life and futures. Without memory of who she was, who she is, or where she's located, all she can remember is that HOME is ABOVE.

Explore a beautiful and melancholy hand-drawn world inspired by the art of Tsutomu Nihei's Blame! and Aposimz. With only your wits and a one-ton coilgun attached to your arm, you must navigate the lower layers of the Follicle, an immense superstructure that seems to extend endlessly both in space and time.

name: Fantasy Fighters: Historic Fighters
description: Historic Fighters is a turn-based game that allows you to play with a historically themed class of your choice in a fantasy battle setting.

name: Dora the Explorer: Lost and Found Adventure
